{"lemma":"وَجَباتُ","slug":"وَجَباتُ","root":"#.ج.ب","root_slug":"_-ج-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ج-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n41665"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"meal, repast"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"menu"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root و ج ب (w j b), indicating necessity."},"ipa":["/wad͡ʒ.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41665","headword_ar":"وَجْبَةٌ","root":"wjb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaba","text_ar":"وَجَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ it fell down, &c., ” q. v. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bijanobihi falotakuni Alwajobapu","text_ar":"بِجَنْبِهِ فَلْتَكُنِ الوَجْبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a proverb, (S,) [("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May a disease be"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God afflict him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smite him, with a disease"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his side, and may falling down upon the ground, and dying, happen"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be the result thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":") ! i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bjnbh dA'N fltkn Alwjbh bh","text_ar":"بجنبه داءٌ فلتكن الوجبه به"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaAhu All~`hu","text_ar":"رَمَاهُ اللّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidaA'K bjnbh Alx","text_ar":"بِدَاءٍ بجنبه الخ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Freytag, Arab. Prov. i. 156)]. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajobapN","text_ar":"وَجْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A falling with a sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"noise, such as that produced by the fall of a wall"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) [see 1, where it is given as an inf. n. unrestricted to the signification of a single act:] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound of a thing falling"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and producing a sound such as above mentioned."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajabahN","text_ar":"وَجَبَهٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An eating but once in the course of a day and night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an eating but once in a day until the like eating in the following day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) an inf. n. (Lh) [restricted to the signification of a single act]: you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yaA^okulu wajobapF","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَاْكُلُ وَجْبَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one eats but once"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the course of the day and night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SayoramN","text_ar":"صَيْرَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  In a trad. respecting the expiation of an oath, it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuToEimu","text_ar":"يُطْعِمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$arapa masaAkiyna wajobapF waAHidapF","text_ar":"عَشَرَةَ مَسَاكِينَ وَجْبَةً وَاحِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He shall feed ten poor men with a meal sufficient for a day and a night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Lh","T"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}